==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pettifogger
<hw>Pet"ti*fog`ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A lawyer who
deals in petty cases; an attorney whose methods are mean and tricky; an
inferior lawyer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>pettifogger</qex> was lord chancellor.</q>
<rj><qau>Macaulay.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pettifoggery</ent>⟦br⟧
